\section*{Performing Suctioning}
- Talk to the mother (parents) about the procedure.
- Put the baby in a slightly extended position
- For manual suctioning using the penguin/bulb sucker;
1. Squeeze the sucker and introduce it into the mouth
2. Release the sucker while in the mouth to create negative pressure
3. Suck the secretions out and pour the secretions on a gauze
![](https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2025_09_22_19dbcf4d7158f6028790g-32.jpg?height=686&width=798&top_left_y=1116&top_left_x=54)
