\section*{Performing Suctioning using Wide Bore Sucker}
- When using a suction machine with the wide bore sucker;
1. Connect the wide bore sucker to the suction machine
2. Set the pressures at $80-100 \mathrm{~mm} / \mathrm{Hg}$
3. Only suck what is visible in the mouth
